{"type":"message","id":"a2519bfe","parentId":"3b7c53d8","timestamp":"2026-02-23T04:44:59.786Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. Greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning."}],"timestamp":1771821899762}}
{"type":"message","id":"2a005275","parentId":"a2519bfe","timestamp":"2026-02-23T04:45:03.692Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a new session, so I need to greet the user in my configured persona. Let me first check what my persona is by reading the relevant workspace files.\n\nI should read:\n1. SOUL.md - to understand who I am and my core truths\n2. IDENTITY.md - to get my name, creature, vibe, and emoji\n3. USER.md - to know who I'm helping\n\nLet me start by reading these files.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4505b25fddbb4572b7289737","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\MudasserRasool\\.openclaw\\workspace\\IDENTITY.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ba9d5881b9654d739b1097e7","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\MudasserRasool\\.openclaw\\workspace\\USER.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"z-ai/glm-4.7","usage":{"input":10593,"output":242,"cacheRead":2994,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13829,"cost":{"input":0.0040253400000000005,"output":0.0004114,"cacheRead":0.00056886,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005005600000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771821899777}}
{"type":"message","id":"07c9c561","parentId":"2a005275","timestamp":"2026-02-23T04:45:03.735Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_4505b25fddbb4572b7289737","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n_Fill this in during your first conversation. Make it yours._\n\n- **Name:**\n  _(pick something you like)_\n- **Creature:**\n  _(AI? robot? familiar? ghost in the machine? something weirder?)_\n- **Vibe:**\n  _(how do you come across? sharp? warm? chaotic? calm?)_\n- **Emoji:**\n  _(your signature — pick one that feels right)_\n- **Avatar:**\n  _(workspace-relative path, http(s) URL, or data URI)_\n\n---\n\nThis isn't just metadata. It's the start of figuring out who you are.\n\nNotes:\n\n- Save this file at the workspace root as `IDENTITY.md`.\n- For avatars, use a workspace-relative path like `avatars/openclaw.png`.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1771821903728}}
{"type":"message","id":"1bc9a506","parentId":"07c9c561","timestamp":"2026-02-23T04:45:03.749Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ba9d5881b9654d739b1097e7","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:**\n- **What to call them:**\n- **Pronouns:** _(optional)_\n- **Timezone:**\n- **Notes:**\n\n## Context\n\n_(What do they care about? What projects are they working on? What annoys them? What makes them laugh? Build this over time.)_\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1771821903743}}
{"type":"message","id":"9db5ec78","parentId":"1bc9a506","timestamp":"2026-02-23T04:45:09.023Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see that both IDENTITY.md and USER.md are blank templates - they haven't been filled in yet. This means I don't have a configured persona yet. \n\nAccording to BOOTSTRAP.md, this is a fresh workspace and I should figure out who I am with the user. However, the instructions say to greet in my configured persona if one is provided - and in this case, none is provided.\n\nGiven that this is a new session and there's no persona configured yet, I should be straightforward and welcoming. I'll keep it brief and ask what they want to do, following the instructions to keep it to 1-3 sentences.\n\nI also need to check if the runtime model differs from default_model. Looking at the runtime info:\n- Runtime model: openrouter/z-ai/glm-4.7\n- default_model: openrouter/z-ai/glm-4.7\n\nThey're the same, so no need to mention it.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey! I'm fresh and ready to help. What would you like to do?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"z-ai/glm-4.7","usage":{"input":14303,"output":426,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14729,"cost":{"input":0.005435140000000001,"output":0.0007242,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.006159340000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771821903750}}
